Description: This package provides user friendly functions to plot ecosystem information within an ecosystem approach to fisheries management framework.
        	It takes ecosystem information from packages such as gslea (https://github.com/duplisea/gslea) to produce high quality visualizations of the data. 
          It can produce bilingual graph annotations using rosettafish (https://github.com/pbs-assess/rosettafish).
